{"tid":1105340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"變態男報復未婚妻　性侵她愛犬致重傷安樂死","createTime":"2019-04-13T20:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T06:34:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"af6f1150916c678a7e136b31b514679fa9918284","tid":1105340,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T20:48:00.000Z","msg":"竟然做出如此人神共憤的事！美國一名52歲的男子因未婚妻不回家又不接他電話，喝了酒後起了報復心態，竟狠心性侵未婚妻的愛犬，導致小狗嚴重創傷，最後需人道毀滅安樂死。美國法院近日宣判該男子只需入獄60天以及緩刑3年等，有指判刑過輕。<br />\n《鏡報》報導，美國奧勒岡州一名52歲男子洛佩茲（Fidel Lopez）於去年11月18日，當晚因未婚妻不回家又不接他電話，喝得爛醉後起了報復心態，竟向未婚妻的愛犬埃斯特雷亞（Estrella）下手。未婚妻回家在沙發底下找到愛犬，發現背部有許多傷痕，而且流很多血，立即帶愛犬到獸醫診所急救，但因為傷勢過重不得不人道安樂死。<br />\n未婚妻認為事件相當可疑，並回想起當時洛佩茲曾提及對人獸交有興趣，還曾經要求她去買一隻體型更大的狗，因此懷疑洛佩茲性虐待愛犬，逐而要求獸醫為愛犬進行性侵檢驗，結果證實愛犬曾遭到性侵，體內果真採集到洛佩茲的DNA。未婚妻在悲痛及憤怒之下，打電話向警察報案，洛佩茲最終遭到逮捕。<br />\n洛佩茲承認性虐未婚妻的愛犬是為了報仇，由於他過往沒有前科刑事紀錄，雖然被起訴一級加重虐待動物和性侵動物等重罪，但最高刑期只能被判60天。洛佩茲最後於當地時間周三（10日），被法官判處入獄服刑60天，以及緩刑3年、賠償500美元（約15,415元台幣）給未婚妻，加上15年內不得再養狗，以及強制接受心理治療。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190414/640_04908b6becb9ae7327a61faa5556f38e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190414%2F640_04908b6becb9ae7327a61faa5556f38e.jpg&h=cacaf559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190414/1550232/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190414%2F1550232%2F&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=2023b8c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190414%2F1550232%2F&h=d94d8acd\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190414/1550232/</a>"},{"pid":"451d60468e2e078d509bf861692158fcc3d7182a","tid":1105340,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T22:31:49.000Z","msg":"墨乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d90456084f159c9d06ee7c2576b12e51644012","tid":1105340,"uid":160263,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T22:38:20.000Z","msg":"我的天..."},{"pid":"f7cb57630233e4914ec221009c1df9cfc28f31af","tid":1105340,"uid":101110,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T22:42:41.000Z","msg":"肯定條友報復心態，坐完會繼續老強動物<br />\n但又廢到唔敢搞人類，只可以搞比佢弱嘅物種<br />\n屌你老母正人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35401a76397475b51033a05bc9030aeaa3a97320","tid":1105340,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7cb57630233e4914ec221009c1df9cfc28f31af","tid":1105340,"uid":101110,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T22:42:41.000Z","msg":"肯定條友報復心態，坐完會繼續老強動物<br />\n但又廢到唔敢搞人類，只可以搞比佢弱嘅物種<br />\n屌你老母正人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa6c99b63928417e6e144abd9034fd1109297ed","tid":1105340,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"如果條狗大Ｄ，可能大學都happy"},{"pid":"062292ec4c8cb32cec30fbdf8ae277590aacbb0b","tid":1105340,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9aa6c99b63928417e6e144abd9034fd1109297ed","tid":1105340,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"如果條狗大Ｄ，可能大學都happy"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:37:09.000Z","msg":"大家"},{"pid":"e96457029061baba2d47de5569007c33e098693c","tid":1105340,"uid":177288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:44:05.000Z","msg":"好彩未結婚"},{"pid":"f17148b559779d3abfc36db0abe555d30ac7e5df","tid":